use InputOutput
use Utils
alias display >>
alias "I want you to print" >>

I want you to print "Hello! and welcome in this mini game..."
wait for 3 seconds
choose a random number between 1 and 1000
remember it as ChosenNumber
display "I've chosen a number, try and guess it"
this is the line Attempt
ask
remember it as Answer
is Answer| smaller than ChosenNumber ?
if so go to TryGreater
is Answer| greater than ChosenNumber ?
if so go to TrySmaller
is Answer| equal to ChosenNumber ?
if so go to Bravo

this is the line TryGreater
display "Try a higher number"
go to Attempt

this is the line TrySmaller
display "Nope, try smaller"
go to Attempt

this is the line Bravo
display "Well done !"
quit
